headline: China property sales forecast cut by S&P as market slump deepens
summary: Investing.com -- S&P Global Ratings has downgraded its forecast for China's property sales in 2026, now predicting a 10% to 14% decline compared to its earlier October estimate of a 5% to 8% drop.
